{"tid":1262731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲I罩杯櫻花女職員辣曬上空照　2年拍17部無碼片遭逮","createTime":"2019-06-27T23:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:31:07.000Z","uid":35519,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ad392587b1628d209ba2fea9e88b8a82429280","tid":1262731,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T23:27:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">22歲I罩杯櫻花女職員辣曬上空照<br />\n2年拍17部無碼片遭逮</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PvqgpGM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPvqgpGM.jpg&h=9f3ff506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0J4tgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0J4tgM.jpg&h=5d404995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYquEos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYquEos.jpg&h=88a98462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲福田美姬的照片在推特上瘋傳。（圖／翻攝自推特／@koku_byakunews）<br />\n<br />\n日本22歲女子福田美姬因為在網路上傳露點影片，被京都府的警察逮捕，進一步追查，發現她竟然是長崎縣某公立學校的行政人員，光是2016年8月到今年2月間就發布17部不雅影片。而福田美姬遭逮一事也在推特上掀起熱烈討論，小有名氣的她很快就被網友搜出照片，甚至還有人貼出部分不雅照片的截圖。<br />\n<br />\n根據《朝日新聞》報導，警方調查，福田美姬去年8月15日自行拍攝兩段露出性器官的影片，沒有做任何處理就上傳到網路，雖然該網站設有成人投稿專區，但任何人都可以免費觀看前一分鐘，如果還想看後續，就得花錢購買點數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1P98UvD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1P98UvD.jpg&h=cf2ee0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲福田美姬經營的網站帳號已經清空。（圖／翻攝自影片網站）<br />\n<br />\n警方透過網路巡邏發現福田美姬涉嫌散播猥褻影片，進一步追查發現她竟然是長崎縣某公立學校的行政人員，從2016年8月到今年2月間，一共上傳17部不雅的無碼影片，24日隨即依法將人逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n雖然福田美姬的推特內容只開放給追蹤的粉絲觀看，網站上的不雅影片也已經全數刪除，但在網路上小有名氣的她還是被肉搜出照片。她在推特上自稱20歲、H罩杯，在影片網站則聲稱是21歲、I罩杯，平時自拍似乎習慣戴口罩或用貼圖、手遮住口鼻，不過，她也經常大方展現好身材，或上傳上空清涼照到推特，如今被逮，過往的「黑歷史」也通通被挖出，在推特上掀起網友們熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc1fb3ba5b1fcbc217504d1cb1286a4e50be034","tid":1262731,"uid":63588,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T23:42:26.000Z","msg":"咁肉酸"},{"pid":"7ef3f77e7cc101ae709f2a73a2376128b5f514a8","tid":1262731,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T23:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6936c08e32a126369a6795076a073a1f11ed6b","tid":1262731,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T23:53:46.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8d0c587d4db58f7abf7020ee12a096e3baa0cd1f","tid":1262731,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc117487c2a9db32dae47421a19886f425784a5","tid":1262731,"uid":34174,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"警方透過網路巡邏發現福田美姬涉嫌散播猥褻影片<br />\n= 打正旗號睇av?"},{"pid":"b80c78d334c501e49fd9628f091d07b85289f6ef","tid":1262731,"uid":140523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"199aed433b864027f07e77f10fa6cbba4ab6d6e0","tid":1262731,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:39:34.000Z","msg":"正皮俾btw果幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e65b69c6f2599678c4611e07faad8a9afd68eaa","tid":1262731,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc117487c2a9db32dae47421a19886f425784a5","tid":1262731,"uid":34174,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"警方透過網路巡邏發現福田美姬涉嫌散播猥褻影片<br />\n= 打正旗號睇av?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6057ad119a5624fbb1abbc4297f5f4bf87543e3","tid":1262731,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{